taxableTurnover.error.mandatory = Enter the business’s taxable turnover
taxableTurnover.error.nonNumeric = Enter the turnover using numbers 0 to 9
taxableTurnover.error.decimals = Enter a number with a maximum of 2 decimal places
taxableTurnover.error.negative = You must enter a positive number
taxableTurnover.error.maximum = You can not enter a number greater than {0}

nextTaxableTurnover.title = What is the business’s expected taxable turnover for the next 12 months?

optionOwesMoney.title = Does the business owe any money?
optionOwesMoney.text.1 = We need to know if the business owes any money for services or supplies that relate to its activities.

